<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;"><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Felhaszn&aacute;l&aacute;si Felt&eacute;telek</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ez a dokumentum tartalmazza az&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">ABCMobile O&Uuml;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;(a tov&aacute;bbiakban: ABC Mobile) &aacute;ltal k&iacute;n&aacute;lt term&eacute;kek &eacute;s / vagy szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sok (a tov&aacute;bbiakban: Szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sok) haszn&aacute;lat&aacute;t szab&aacute;lyoz&oacute; &Aacute;ltal&aacute;nos Szerződ&eacute;si Felt&eacute;teleket. ABCMobile&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">O&Uuml;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">14710834</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">; С&iacute;m: Harju maakond, Tallinn, Peterburi tee 71-318, 11415, Estonia. A Szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sok haszn&aacute;lat&aacute;val &eacute;s / vagy az ABC Mobile term&eacute;kek b&aacute;rmelyik&eacute;nek telep&iacute;t&eacute;s&eacute;vel a felhaszn&aacute;l&oacute; megerős&iacute;ti, hogy bet&ouml;lt&ouml;tte a 18. &eacute;let&eacute;v&eacute;t, &eacute;s elfogadja, hogy a jelen Felt&eacute;telek, valamint Adatv&eacute;delmi Ir&aacute;nyelvek jogilag k&ouml;telezőek. Megjegyz&eacute;s vagy k&eacute;rd&eacute;s eset&eacute;n k&eacute;rj&uuml;k, k&uuml;ldj&ouml;n e-mailt a&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:abcmobile.hu@silverlines.info" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">abcmobile.hu@silverlines.info</span></a><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;c&iacute;mre.</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&Aacute;ltal&aacute;nos Felt&eacute;telek</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">A Szolg&aacute;ltat&oacute; kiz&aacute;r minden felelőss&eacute;get vagy garanci&aacute;t az inform&aacute;ci&oacute;k pontoss&aacute;g&aacute;ra, relevanci&aacute;j&aacute;ra vagy minős&eacute;g&eacute;re vonatkoz&oacute;an, &eacute;s csak sz&oacute;rakoztat&oacute; c&eacute;lokat szolg&aacute;l. A Szolg&aacute;ltat&oacute; nem v&aacute;llal felelőss&eacute;get semmilyen szem&eacute;lynek vagy szervezetnek, semmilyen vesztes&eacute;g&eacute;rt vagy k&aacute;r&eacute;rt, (bele&eacute;rtve, de nem kiz&aacute;r&oacute;lag, fizikai, szellemi, k&uuml;l&ouml;nleges vagy k&ouml;zvetett) amelyet a Szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;son kereszt&uuml;l ny&uacute;jtott b&aacute;rmilyen t&aacute;j&eacute;koztat&aacute;s &eacute;s/vagy javaslat, tan&aacute;cs okozott, vagy a Szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;s haszn&aacute;lat&aacute;nak eredm&eacute;nye, f&uuml;ggetlen&uuml;l att&oacute;l, hogy hanyags&aacute;gb&oacute;l, balesetből vagy b&aacute;rmilyen m&aacute;s okb&oacute;l sz&aacute;rmazik-e</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Az eg&eacute;szs&eacute;g&uuml;gyi &aacute;llapottal kapcsolatos tan&aacute;csokat enged&eacute;llyel rendelkező orvosnak kell ellenőriznie, mielőtt cselekedne.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Emelt d&iacute;jas szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;s</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">A szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sok ig&eacute;nybev&eacute;tel&eacute;hez vagy a sz&aacute;mlafizetőnek kell lennie, vagy a sz&aacute;mlafizető enged&eacute;ly&eacute;re van sz&uuml;ks&eacute;ge a h&iacute;v&aacute;s kezdem&eacute;nyez&eacute;s&eacute;hez. A szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;s ig&eacute;nybev&eacute;tele Magyarorsz&aacute;gon bel&uuml;l 1270 ft/SMS (&Aacute;F&Aacute;-t tartalmazza).&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Jogi nyilatkozat, szerzői jog &eacute;s egy&eacute;b felt&eacute;telek</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Minden term&eacute;k &eacute;s szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;s szerzői jogi v&eacute;delem al&aacute; esik, &eacute;s nem szabad m&aacute;solni, megosztani, szerkeszteni, m&oacute;dos&iacute;tani vagy terjeszteni.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Az ABC Mobile fenntartja mag&aacute;nak a jogot, hogy ideiglenesen vagy v&eacute;glegesen m&oacute;dos&iacute;tsa vagy megsz&uuml;ntesse a ny&uacute;jtott szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sokat, ha:</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Vissza&eacute;lt a szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sunkkal valamilyen m&oacute;don;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Vissza&eacute;lt a c&eacute;g alkalmazottaival vagy az olvas&oacute;kkal;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">- Csal&aacute;st k&ouml;vetett el.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Az ABC Mobile fenntartja mag&aacute;nak a jogot, hogy a szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;s jav&iacute;t&aacute;sa &eacute;rdek&eacute;ben m&oacute;dos&iacute;tsa a term&eacute;keket vagy szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sokat. Javasoljuk, hogy rendszeresen ellenőrizze a webhelyet a szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sokkal kapcsolatos friss&iacute;t&eacute;sek megtekint&eacute;s&eacute;hez.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ez az oldal olyan linkeket tartalmazhat, amelyek harmadik f&eacute;lhez tartoznak, &eacute;s amelyek nem kapcsol&oacute;dnak az ABC Mobile-hoz. Az ezen oldalakon megjelen&iacute;tett tartalom nem az ABC Mobile felelőss&eacute;ge, &eacute;s nem t&aacute;mogatja ezeket a weboldalakat vagy szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sokat.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&Ouml;n v&aacute;llalja, hogy teljes m&eacute;rt&eacute;kben k&aacute;rtalan&iacute;tja &eacute;s mentes&iacute;ti az ABC Mobile-ot, annak tiszts&eacute;gviselőit, igazgat&oacute;it, alkalmazottait, &uuml;gyn&ouml;keit &eacute;s szolg&aacute;ltat&oacute;it minden olyan k&ouml;lts&eacute;ggel, kiad&aacute;ssal, vesztes&eacute;ggel, k&aacute;rral, k&ouml;vetel&eacute;ssel &eacute;s felelőss&eacute;ggel kapcsolatban, amely az ABC Mobile webhely haszn&aacute;lat&aacute;val, vagy a szolg&aacute;ltat&aacute;sban val&oacute; r&eacute;szv&eacute;tellel kapcsolatban felmer&uuml;lhet.</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ir&aacute;nyad&oacute; Jog.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br></span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">A jelen &Aacute;ltal&aacute;nos Szerződ&eacute;si Felt&eacute;teleket a magyar jog szab&aacute;lyozza, &eacute;s &Ouml;n, valamint az&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">ABCMobile O&Uuml;</span><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;beleegyezik abba, hogy a Magyar B&iacute;r&oacute;s&aacute;g kiz&aacute;r&oacute;lagos joghat&oacute;s&aacute;ga al&aacute; tartozik.</span></p>
